Do chrome extension -> then do website (not app)
Replika chatbot on webiste (using open-source code)


Chrome Extension: (https://thoughtbot.com/blog/how-to-make-a-chrome-extension)
  Enter a fact (copy + paste)
  Googles that fact
  Returns a % of how sure it is of that fact and a conclusion
 
Website:
  Replika Chatbot (https://www.reddit.com/r/replika/comments/bg6v0n/replika_is_open_source/; https://www.wired.com/story/replika-open-source/)
  Enter a fact (copy + paste)
  Googles that fact
  Returns a % of how sure it is of that fact and a conclusion
  
